snippet: World number ones Novak Djokovic and Serena Williams completed a clean sweep for tennis as they won the Laureus Sportsman and Sportswoman of the Year awards on Monday....
lead_paragraph: World number ones Novak Djokovic and Serena Williams completed a clean sweep for tennis as they won the Laureus Sportsman and Sportswoman of the Year awards on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Djokovic, Serena Win Top Laureus Awards for Dominating Tennis in 2015
headline.main: Djokovic, Serena Win Top Laureus Awards for Dominating Tennis in 2015
